---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-3xl">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About This Archive</h1>
  <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
    Welcome! This site chronicles my learning journey through various projects,
    experiments, and the lessons I picked up along the way.
  </p>
  <section class="prose dark:prose-invert">
    <h2>Why?</h2>
    <p>
      I built this archive to document not just what I built, but <strong
        >how</strong
      > and <strong>why</strong> I built it. Each project is a story of growth, mistakes,
      and new skills.
    </p>
    <h2>What You'll Find</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Project summaries and details</li>
      <li>Tags and topics for each project</li>
      <li>Key takeaways and lessons learned</li>
      <li>Links to code and resources</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

